<paragraph id="BD668C89C3B33F71CA074D7C2A46B8A4" pageId="17" pageNumber="28">Distribution, habitat, and remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="390F20383151175B39208AAA1D5B3847" pageId="17" pageNumber="28">This species occurs in wet lowland forest. It is recorded from Nicaragua, Costa Rica, French Guiana, Guyana, Venezuela, Colombia, Peru, Bolivia, and Brazil (PA, PE, ES).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
